    "data_flow": "Writes enter through API → Primary PostgreSQL. Changes propagate asynchronously: (1) streaming replication to read replicas, (2) CDC/triggers to search index and aggregation store. Reads are routed by query type: simple lookups → replica, search → search index, aggregations → aggregation store. Archival job periodically moves old data from primary to cold storage, keeping the active dataset bounded.",
    "patterns_used": [
